<body>
    <div class="upar">
        <a href="./login.ejs">
            <img src="images/FoundIt! logo.png" alt="">
        </a>
    </div>

    <div class="main-container">
        <div class="flexi">
            <div class="content">
                <p>
                    Welcome to FoundIt!<br><br>
                    Have you misplaced something on the vibrant campus of VIT-AP? Fear not, because FoundIt! is your trusted ally in the
                    search for lost treasuresâ€”excluding, of course, your elusive study buddy ;) Whether it's a forgotten notebook left in the
                    library, a missing pair of headphones from the cafeteria, or something entirely unexpected, we're here to assist you in
                    rediscovering what matters most to you. <br><br>Let's turn lost into found, one search at a time!
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="loghin">
